      • JTA_TRANSACTION_TIMEOUT

        static final String JTA_TRANSACTION_TIMEOUT
        Timeout for JTA transactions. If the transaction is still in the "active" state after this time (counting from begin()), it is automatically rolled back.

        Constant Field Values

      • LOCAL_WEBLOGIC_HOME

        static final String LOCAL_WEBLOGIC_HOME
        Path to local WebLogic home. This property is used in Remote container to gather WLST dependencies needed for remote communication with WebLogic instance. WebLogic needs to be installed locally even for remote calls.
